        </h2>
        <p class="mt-[18px] text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-muted)]">Transparent flat-fee pricing with zero delivery brokerage. No hidden charges — what you see is what you pay.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="equity-reveal overflow-hidden rounded-[14px] border border-[var(--color-n400)]">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-[15.5px]">
